People drop extra gold when killed depending on the killer's health after the fight. In teams game, it depends on the average health of the team.
-80%-100%: None
-60%-80%: 2
-40%-60%: 4
-30%-40%: 6
-15%-30%: 8
-0%-15%: 10

This skript uses the variables from D4's team manager. Edits of D4's skript will probably work too.

Commands:
Operators only:
/refill enable/on/true/start    - Enables the scenario
/refill disable/off/false/stop  - Disables the scenario
/refill toggle                  - Toggles the state of the scenario (enabled/disabled)
